withdrawal, payouts support and other UI updates (1.5d)\\\\n- Proposal testing call (1h)\\\\n\\\\nTotal: 42.5h\\\\n\\\\nWeek 2 (4 Mar to 10 Mar)\\\\n- Move alpha testers reported bugs to [sheets](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uaKGpIJl_mk1lpeFLAImv5s9XSvsR_s-kRzOKhuljwQ/edit#gid=0) and fix them (1.5d)\\\\n- Call with Vadim regarding bugs (0.5h)\\\\n- Fix posts feed [#685](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/685) figure out way to get aggregate count from QueryAPI and add offset support [#686](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/686) reply and like notifications, show author instead of devhub.near account in notification, discuss with Vadim about contract implementation [#683](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/683) (1d)\\\\n- Make proposals flow mobile responsive  [#683](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/683) (1.5d)\\\\n- Team call (0.5h)\\\\n- UI session with Ori (1h)\\\\n- UI enhancements [#693](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/693) (1.5d)\\\\n- KYC integration with different states [#693](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/693) (6h)\\\\n\\\\nTotal: 40h\\\\n\\\\nWeek 4 (18 Mar to 24 Mar)\\\\n- CSS updates , move new bugs to sheets reported by testers and fixes, figure out issue with copy to clipboard (1d)\\\\n- Tested notification on near.org and created issue [#717](https://github.com/near/near-discovery-components/issues/717)  (3h)\\\\n- Test and Review proposal filter PR (1h)\\\\n- Update data (show comment/new/updated proposal) after redirection for my near wallet [#693](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/693) (5h)\\\\n- Team sync (0.5h)\\\\n- UI session with Ori (1.5h)\\\\n- Update UI as per Ori\\\\u{2019}s suggestions to make it more similar to sigma design and add info banners, update links [#696](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/696) (5h)\\\\n- Review PRs (1h)\\\\n- Fix critical bugs [#701](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/701) and UI enhancements [#702](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-bos/pull/702) (4h)\\\\n- Update data (show comment/new/updated proposal) after redirection for my popup wallets/ don\\\\\\'t ask again {"id": 13, "body": {"name": "Expenses for DevRel Events March 2024", "summary": "These are the expenses for ETHDenver and ETHGlobal London", "category": "Events & Hackathons", "timeline": {"status": "DRAFT"}, "supervisor": "yarotska.near", "description": "Number of Days: 17 days\\\\nNumber of Events; 2\\\\nCosts Covered: Hotels, Transportation, Plane Tickets and Food\\\\n\\\\nETHDenver (Feb 22 - March 04): \\\\nFood: $324.97\\\\nTransportation:\\\\t$703.40\\\\nPlane Tickets:\\\\t$633.19\\\\nSub-Total: $1661.56\\\\n\\\\nResponsibilities:\\\\n\\\\n* Support for ETHDenver Hackathon support including workshops, talks, and direct engagement and technical support with developers.\\\\n* Support for Side Events (DevHub Side Event, Pragma, SuperMoon, Chain Abstraction Day) this support includes workshops, talks, and booth work\\\\n* Support for Main Event includes booth work, direct engagement and technical support with developers, and engagement with general ETHDenver participants.\\\\n\\\\nETH Global London (March 11 - March 18): \\\\nFood: $508.30\\\\nTransportation: $444.73\\\\nHotel: $1,860.42 (shared room for 2 devrels)\\\\nPlane Tickets: $854.90\\\\nSub-Total: $3668.435\\\\n\\\\nResponsibilities:\\\\n\\\\n* Support for ETHGlobal Hackathon  including workshops, talks, and direct engagement and technical support with developers.\\\\n* Support for Side Events (Pragma) booth work, direct engagement and technical support with developers, and engagement with general ETHGlobal participants.\\\\n\\\\n**Total: $5329.91**\\\\n\\\\nAll invoices have been made available to NEAR Foundation.\\\\n\\\\n", "linked_proposals": [], "receiver_account": "bpolania.near", "requested_sponsor": "neardevdao.near", "proposal_body_version": "V0", "requested_sponsorship_usd_amount": "5330", "requested_sponsorship_paid_in_currency": "USDC"}, "labels": []}

{"body": {"name": "Bounty payout for NEAR Hacks and Autonomous Agents hackathons", "summary": "This is a proposal that covers the bounty payouts for Near bounties at 2 hackathons hosted by various teams in the ecosystem.", "category": "Events & Hackathons", "timeline": {"status": "DRAFT"}, "supervisor": "bpolania.near", "description": "**NEAR Hacks Information**\\\\n[The NEAR Hacks](https://nearhacks.hackerearth.com/) is a hackathon sponsored by NEAR India in January, 2024. NEAR India partnered up with HackerEarth platform to host a hackathon as a follow-up for their presence at ETHIndia. 1500+ developers were onboarded by the platform but unfortunately NEAR India was discontinued shortly after the hackathon started as part of NEAR Foundation\\\\\\'s reorg efforts. \\\\n\\\\nThe hackathon came to an end on February 29th, 2024, and the platform selected a short list of 30 finalists. NEAR DevHub\\\\\\'s DevRel team reviewed the submissions and selected 4 winning teams across 2 tracks of the hackathon.\\\\n\\\\nDev Track winners:\\\\n* NEARVision:Enhanced Analytics Dashboard For The NEAR Blockchain Ecosystem\\\\n* RubikUI\\\\n\\\\nProduct Track winners:\\\\n* Step Into NFT Adventure Turn Steps Into Crypto And Boost Local Business\\\\n* HonorHub\\\\n\\\\nAll of the submission pages including the winning ones can be reviewed [here](https://nearhacks.hackerearth.com/).\\\\n\\\\nI\\\\\\'m requesting $USDT 4000 to administed the bounty payouts through NEAR Heroes platform. Each winning team will get $1000.\\\\n\\\\n**Autonomous Agents Information**\\\\n[Autonomous Agent: AI x Web3 Hackathon](https://autonomous-agent.devpost.com/) is a hackathon hosted by Edge in February, 2024. Pagoda offered a bounty for this hackathon, and NEAR DevHub supported the hosts in setting up their event.\\\\n\\\\nThe hackathon came to an end on March 22nd, and the winners will be announced on April 2nd. One of the winners will receive a Near bounty worth of $1000. I\\\\\\'m requesting $USDT 1000 to administed the bounty payouts through NEAR Heroes platform.", "linked_proposals": [], "receiver_account": "devhub-payouts.near", "requested_sponsor": "neardevdao.near", "proposal_body_version": "V0", "requested_sponsorship_usd_amount": "5000", "requested_sponsorship_paid_in_currency": "USDT"}, "labels": []}
